## <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tarikul-Islam-Anik/Animated-Fluent-Emojis/master/Emojis/Objects/Bar%20Chart.png" width="30"> &nbsp;GitHub Analytics

<div align="center">

<img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Public_Repos-{{ profile.public_repos }}-{{ config.theme.accent }}?style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white" alt="Repos">
<img src="https://img.shields.io/github/followers/{{ username }}?label=Followers&style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white&color={{ config.theme.accent }}" alt="Followers">
<img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Following-{{ profile.following }}-{{ config.theme.accent }}?style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white" alt="Following">

</div>

{% if top_languages %}
<div align="center">
<h4>Top Languages (by repo bytes)</h4>

{% for lang in top_languages %}
<img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/{{ lang.name | replace(' ', '_') }}-{{ lang.percent }}%25-{{ config.theme.accent }}?style=flat-square" alt="{{ lang.name }}">
{% endfor %}

</div>
{% endif %}

<br>

<div align="center">
  <img src="https://streak-stats.demolab.com/?user={{ username }}&theme=github-dark-blue&hide_border=true&background={{ config.theme.bg }}&ring={{ config.theme.accent }}&fire={{ config.theme.accent }}&currStreakLabel={{ config.theme.accent }}&sideLabels={{ config.theme.text }}&dates={{ config.theme.text }}80" alt="GitHub Streak" width="55%">
</div>

<br>

<!-- Contribution Activity Graph -->
<div align="center">
  <img src="https://github-readme-activity-graph.vercel.app/graph?username={{ username }}&theme=github-compact&hide_border=true&bg_color={{ config.theme.bg }}&color={{ config.theme.accent }}&line={{ config.theme.accent }}&point={{ config.theme.text }}&area=true&area_color={{ config.theme.bg_secondary }}" alt="Activity Graph" width="95%">
</div>

<br>

<!-- Snake Contribution Animation -->
<div align="center">
  <picture>
    <source media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)" srcset="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/{{ username }}/{{ username }}/main/output/github-snake-dark.svg" />
    <source media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)" srcset="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/{{ username }}/{{ username }}/main/output/github-snake.svg" />
    <img alt="Snake animation" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/{{ username }}/{{ username }}/main/output/github-snake-dark.svg" width="95%" />
  </picture>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

## <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tarikul-Islam-Anik/Animated-Fluent-Emojis/master/Emojis/Objects/Lightning.png" width="30"> &nbsp;Recent Activity

{% if events %}
<table>
<tr><th>🎯</th><th>Activity</th><th>Repository</th><th>When</th></tr>
{% for event in events %}
<tr>
  <td align="center">{{ event.emoji }}</td>
  <td>{{ event.description }}</td>
  <td><a href="https://github.com/{{ event.repo }}"><code>{{ event.repo }}</code></a></td>
  <td><sub>{{ event.time_ago }}</sub></td>
</tr>
{% endfor %}
</table>
{% else %}
<p align="center"><em>No recent activity to display.</em></p>
{% endif %}

{% if medium_posts %}
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

## <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tarikul-Islam-Anik/Animated-Fluent-Emojis/master/Emojis/Objects/Newspaper.png" width="30"> &nbsp;Latest from Medium

<div align="center">

{% for post in medium_posts %}
<a href="{{ post.url }}">
  <img src="https://github-readme-medium-recent-article.vercel.app/medium/@{{ config.social.medium }}/{{ loop.index0 }}" alt="{{ post.title }}" width="47%">
</a>
{% if loop.index is even or loop.last %}<br><br>{% else %}&nbsp;{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

</div>

<details>
<summary>&nbsp;<b>All articles</b>&nbsp; <sup>(click to expand)</sup></summary>
<br>

{% for post in medium_posts %}
| <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/-{{ config.theme.bg }}?style=flat-square&logo=medium&logoColor=white" alt="M"> | [**{{ post.title }}**]({{ post.url }}) | <sub>{{ post.date }}</sub> |
{% endfor %}

</details>
{% endif %}

{% if featured_projects %}
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

## <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tarikul-Islam-Anik/Animated-Fluent-Emojis/master/Emojis/Objects/Gem%20Stone.png" width="30"> &nbsp;Featured Projects

<div align="center">

| Project | Description | Language | Stars | Forks |
|---------|-------------|----------|-------|-------|
{% for project in featured_projects %}
| [**{{ project.name }}**]({{ project.url }}) | {{ project.description }} | ![{{ project.language or project.tech }}](https://img.shields.io/badge/-{{ (project.language or project.tech) | replace(' ', '_') }}-{{ config.theme.accent }}?style=flat-square) | ![Stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/{{ project.full_name }}?style=flat-square&color={{ config.theme.accent }}) | ![Forks](https://img.shields.io/github/forks/{{ project.full_name }}?style=flat-square&color={{ config.theme.accent }}) |
{% endfor %}

</div>
{% endif %}

